  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      581.13,
      504.12,
      608.21
    ],
    "text": "Website Introduced for Traffic Management and Parking Facilities During Ruhunu Maha Kataragama Devalaya Esala Perahera",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      622.65,
      502.86,
      663.53
    ],
    "text": "The Information Technology Division of the Sri Lanka Police has introduced a dedicated website to assist devotees travelling to Kataragama for the Ruhunu Maha Kataragama Devalaya Esala Perahera, which is scheduled to be held from 15.07.2026 to 30.07.2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      678.09,
      523.62,
      718.97
    ],
    "text": "The website enables visitors to easily identify available parking facilities in the Kataragama town area and obtain real-time information regarding parking availability during the Perahera period.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      733.55,
      519.64,
      774.43
    ],
    "text": "The platform has been developed with live updates on available parking spaces and provides directions through Google Maps to the nearest available parking location using the most convenient and least congested routes.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      31.91,
      492.29,
      58.99
    ],
    "text": "As an additional feature, contact points and relevant telephone numbers have also been integrated with Google Maps to provide further assistance to the public.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      73.57,
      493.66,
      100.65
    ],
    "text": "This initiative is expected to help reduce traffic congestion in the Kataragama area and minimise inconvenience to devotees and the general public during the Perahera season.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      115.21,
      344.95,
      128.49
    ],
